{"about_the_game":"<strong>Idle Towers</strong> is a survival idle game with tower defense mechanics. Face infinite waves of enemies, upgrade your towers and try to survive as long as you can! Use various prestige and super upgrades to get even more power. Hardcore challenges, customization, rewards, achivements and many more features are waiting for you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2>Upgrade your towers to withstand the increasing onslaught of enemies. An addictive idle gameplay with tower defense mechanins and clicker game math!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HARDCORE</h2>It's a real survival. If you are defeated, you will lose all temporary upgrades and level progress. Invest into permanent upgrades to move forward.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UPGRADES</h2>Buy over a hundred improvements the create the most powerful and impregnable defense. Each upgrade matters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PRESTIGE AND SUPER UPGRADES</h2>Reset your current progress but receive the most valuable upgrades for your towers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PASSIVE INCOME</h2>The game has become too difficult? Go into deep defense and develop passive income. It's up to you how to generate money!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DIFFICULTY TIERS</h2>Complete base levels and find out that it's just the beginning. Only the most persistent players will be able to pass all the challenges!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CUSTOMIZATION</h2>Unlock various color schemes for the interface and other game elements. Customize your towers as you want!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ACHIEVEMENTS AND RANKING</h2>Try to collect all Steam achievements and also conquer the global ranking system where you compete with players from all over the world.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Super Precision","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3190950/e549e93292cbbb7e987a86966ac1453f34ec3f01.jpg"},{"name":"Absolute Destruction","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3190950/e549e93292cbbb7e987a86966